# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Upstream-blocked CVEs in EOL Spring Boot 2.3.9.RELEASE dependencies
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# This project pins Spring Boot 2.3.9.RELEASE (June 2021, EOL since 2022-07).
# The remaining CVEs live in transitive dependencies (Spring Framework 5.2.x,
# Tomcat 9.0.x, Jackson, SnakeYaml 1.26, Hibernate Validator, Logback) that
# cannot be bumped individually while staying on Spring Boot 2.3.9 — the
# Spring Boot BOM locks versions.
#
# Proper fix: upgrade to Spring Boot 3.x (Java 17+). That migration is tracked
# separately (see CLAUDE.md). Until then, every entry below is upstream-blocked.
# Re-check this file after the Spring Boot upgrade lands — most entries will
# disappear automatically.
#
# Upstream tracker: https://spring.io/projects/spring-boot#support

# --- Spring Framework / Spring Boot core (5.2.x → fixed in 5.3+, 6.x) ---
